      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, ¶ 10/5/75. ¶ The honorable R. Ramsay  ¶  ¶ &amp;c  ¶  ¶ &amp;c ¶ Sir ¶  ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you, that on Saturday, the 15th inst, I have to deliver a lecture on industrial plants before...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">75.05.10</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Robert Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">G75/5367, unit 811, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">10/5/75.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable R. Ramsay <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>&amp;c <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>&amp;c</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you, that on Saturday, the 15th inst, I have to deliver a lecture on industrial plants before the Farmers Club at Ballarat, and that it is my intention, if it meets with your approbation, to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>proceed thence to some other places in the western districts,<note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>which I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>wish particularly to examine in reference to the intended school-work on Victorian plants. May I ask, that a rail-way pass be provided me,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotations: by Ramsay on 12 May 1875,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'I will be glad if the practice permits it',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in an unknown hand: '<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <hi rend="underline">Urgent</hi>
                        </seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[Railways] 13/5'. The Railways responded:</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>'<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <hi rend="underline">Immediate</hi>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Under the special circumstances stated the Commissioner authorises the issue a pass in this instance, which I enclose; but I am to add that for the future the travelling expenses of the Govt Botanist must be provided for, &amp; paid to this Department as in the the case of other Govt Officers<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="valediction"
                        style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">John Steavenson</p>
                     <p rend="valediction"
                        style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Secy</p>
                     <p rend="valediction"
                        style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>13.5.75.</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Under Secretary</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Minutes on the file show that the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>pass<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was forwarded to M by the Under Secretary, W. Odgers, on 14 May 1875.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as I have no vote to charge the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>expense<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to, being indeed since February obliged to pay all current daily expenses of the Department, except Assistants salary, out of my private means.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von. Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
